item.title: Cross Country rocks BUCS in Brighton
item.author: Cloudy Carnegie,Liam Smith,Matthew Douthwaite,
item.description: Early on Saturday 31st January a 37 strong team from Imperial Cross Country took the train down to Brighton to compete in the BUCS Cross Country Championships, apprehensively eyeing up the snow from the windows.
